Titolo: 7 dní a 7 nocí

Anno: 1994

Descrizione: 7 dní a 7 nocí (aka Sedm dní a sedm nocí; English: 7 Days and 7 Nights) is a 1994 Czech adventure game released on MS-DOS through Petr Vochozka's Vochozka Trading brand, and published by Pterodon Software. It was the first Czech video game to use Sound Blaster. The game was released in German as 7 Tage, 7 Nächte and in Polish as 7 Dni i 7 Nocy.